==English==

===Noun Phrase===
{{wikipedia}}
'''sentinel event'''

#As defined by the [[w:Joint Commission on Accreditation of Healthcare Organizations|Joint Commission on Accreditation of Healthcare Organizations]], any unanticipated or unusual event in a medical setting which results in death or serious physical injury to a person or persons, specifically including limb loss or gross motor function.

